					[1639] listitem ''
						ListMarker '•'
						StaticText "These gingerbread ninjas have earned their black belts in deliciousness. Crafty Cooking Kits brings you the martial art fan's gingerbread cookie kit. The kit includes classic cookie mix, royal icing mix, candy beads, piping bags, and four (4) ninja cookie cutters. These Ninjabread Gingerbread cookies will put up a fight at your next holiday party. Pass out the icing and let guests decorate their own Christmas party, office party, school party, bake sale, birthday party, baby shower, wedding shower, or surprise party. Have a movie buff who loves classic karate or kung fu movies? The Ninjabread cookies make a great Christmas gift, birthday gift, Secret Santa gift, white elephant gift, wedding gift, or stocking stuffer. Crafty Cooking Kits make great art projects for kids of all ages who love having fun with their food. Grab one for anyone who loves arts and crafts, cake decorating, pastries, baking, cooking, and edible crafting projects. Need to jazz up a party during the year? Bake up a few ninjas for other holiday parties like Memorial Day, 4th of July, or Labor day or even special occasions like a graduation party, retirement party, anniversary or house warming party."
